{"type":"message","id":"84812030","parentId":"f459888c","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:02:46.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the SWE-Agent-Node project status.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a67638c7ed1c4171ad188056","name":"edit","arguments":{"new_string":"#### 2. 自进化系统（Evolver）\n- **状态**：持续运行\n- **目标**：自我改进，减少错误\n- **当前健康评分**：7.5/10（目标 8.5+）\n- **最新进展**：成功解决长会话导致的 429 错误问题（-99.5%）\n- **核心机制**：\n  - R-CCAM 循环（Recognize → Classify → Create → Apply → Monitor）\n  - Pattern Registry（模式库）\n  - Safe Functions（安全函数）\n  - 会话生命周期管理（新增）\n\n**关键教训**：\n- 修复脚本对 ENOENT 错误无效果（LLM 不调用脚本）\n- 需要在工具调用层面修复（修改 read/edit 默认行为）\n- 长会话是 429 错误的主要来源（需定期清理）\n- 会话轮换机制必不可少","old_string":"#### 2. 自进化系统（Evolver）\n- **状态**：持续运行\n- **目标**：自我改进，减少错误\n- **当前健康评分**：7.0/10（目标 8.5+）\n- **核心机制**：\n  - R-CCAM 循环（Recognize → Classify → Create → Apply → Monitor）\n  - Pattern Registry（模式库）\n  - Safe Functions（安全函数）\n\n**关键教训**：\n- 修复脚本对 ENOENT 错误无效果（LLM 不调用脚本）\n- 需要在工具调用层面修复（修改 read/edit 默认行为）\n- 错误高峰期：03:00, 07:00, 09:00, 10:00, 12:50, 15:00-16:00","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":291,"output":418,"cacheRead":25728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26437,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773252153971}}
