{"type":"message","id":"ad65b712","parentId":"2664cb28","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:02:55.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the key lessons section to include the new learning about long sessions.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bac9df0a6c9548b69ea51936","name":"edit","arguments":{"new_string":"## 💡 关键教训与模式\n\n### 1. 长会话管理（2026-03-11 新增）\n\n**429 错误根因**：\n- ❌ 不是单纯的速率限制问题\n- ✅ **超长会话累积请求**是主要原因（20-28 小时会话）\n- ✅ 终止长会话后 429 错误减少 99.5%\n\n**解决方案**：\n- 创建会话生命周期管理 Skill\n- 定期检查并终止 >24 小时的会话\n- 防止单个会话累积过多请求\n\n**关键发现**：\n- 2 个长会话产生 75.8% 的 429 错误\n- 终止后立即见效（错误从 7044.5 降至 33）\n- 需要建立预防机制，不能仅靠临时修复\n\n### 2. 错误处理模式","old_string":"## 💡 关键教训与模式\n\n### 1. 错误处理模式","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":473,"output":267,"cacheRead":25984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26724,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773252166315}}
